title: Revisionist History Season 7: The Experiment Experience
itunes:title: Revisionist History Season 7: The Experiment Experience
description:
Revisionist History is back! And obsessed with ... experiments. Natural experiments. Thought experiments. Failed experiments. Experiments that end up in salt factories and file drawers filled with carbon copies. Not to mention experimental endings to Hollywood classics and a deep dive involving the sitcom Will and Grace. Season 7 gets underway June 30, with episodes available a week early for Pushkin+ subscribers. Find out more at Pushkin.fm. 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
